ltName":"Dendron"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":24,"offset":2846},"end":{"line":26,"column":57,"offset":2879},"indent":[]},"value":"开发记录.2026-05-07-多语言字库与稳定性开发纪要"}],"anchors":{"多语言字库与稳定性开发纪要":{"type":"header","text":"多语言字库与稳定性开发纪要","value":"多语言字库与稳定性开发纪要","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"1-多语言与字库":{"type":"header","text":"1. 多语言与字库","value":"1-多语言与字库","line":15,"column":0,"depth":2},"11-现象记录时":{"type":"header","text":"1.1 现象（记录时）","value":"11-现象记录时","line":17,"column":0,"depth":3},"12-根因韩文":{"type":"header","text":"1.2 根因（韩文）","value":"12-根因韩文","line":25,"column":0,"depth":3},"13-采取的措施":{"type":"header","text":"1.3 采取的措施","value":"13-采取的措施","line":30,"column":0,"depth":3},"14-其它脚本说明已有":{"type":"header","text":"1.4 其它脚本说明（已有）","value":"14-其它脚本说明已有","line":39,"column":0,"depth":3},"15-后续建议字库":{"type":"header","text":"1.5 后续建议（字库）","value":"15-后续建议字库","line":44,"column":0,"depth":3},"2-稳定性data-abort-与按键场景":{"type":"header","text":"2. 稳定性：Data Abort 与按键场景","value":"2-稳定性data-abort-与按键场景","line":51,"column":0,"depth":2},"21-现象":{"type":"header","text":"2.1 现象","value":"21-现象","line":53,"column":0,"depth":3},"22-架构层结论不写实现细节":{"type":"header","text":"2.2 架构层结论（不写实现细节）","value":"22-架构层结论不写实现细节","line":58,"column":0,"depth":3},"23-文档化-bug须后续彻底解决":{"type":"header","text":"2.3 文档化 Bug（须后续彻底解决）","value":"23-文档化-bug须后续彻底解决","line":64,"column":0,"depth":3},"3-涉及路径速查":{"type":"header","text":"3. 涉及路径速查","value":"3-涉及路径速查","line":72,"column":0,"depth":2},"4-后续工作清单":{"type":"header","text":"4. 后续工作清单","value":"4-后续工作清单","line":87,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"x43b2g7jzkj4yilx9xlswpb","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"多语言字库与稳定性开发纪要\">多语言字库与稳定性开发纪要<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#多语言字库与稳定性开发纪要\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"多语言字库与稳定性开发纪要-1\">多语言字库与稳定性开发纪要<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#多语言字库与稳定性开发纪要-1\"></a></h1>\n<p><strong>工程</strong>：<code>bk7252n_sdk-SDK_3.0.76.1_witch_lcd</code>（BK7252N + RT-Thread + LVGL）<br>\n<strong>摘要</strong>：本轮围绕 UI 多语言显示缺陷修复（韩文等）、串口极限操作下的 <strong>Data Abort</strong> 根因分析，以及 Bug 跟踪文档落地。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"1-多语言与字库\">1. 多语言与字库<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#1-多语言与字库\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"11-现象记录时\">1.1 现象（记录时）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#11-现象记录时\"></a></h3>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>语言 ID</th><th>代码</th><th>现象</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>3</td><td>ko</td><td>界面几乎无法正常显示文字（韩文音节大量缺失）</td></tr><tr><td>20</td><td>uk</td><td>曾有「整页无字」讨论；源码侧核对 <code>lv_font_ui_i18n_14</code> 码点与乌克兰语 <code>ui_strings</code> 行可一致，需结合实机固件版本区分「缺字」与「其它运行时问题」</td></tr><tr><td>11 / 16 / 18</td><td>pt / tr / cs</td><td>偶有一两字缺失的讨论；静态核对扩展拉丁字符多在 <code>lv_font_ui_i18n_14</code> 中</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<h3 id=\"12-根因韩文\">1.2 根因（韩文）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#12-根因韩文\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>ui_strings_font()</code> 对 lang <strong>0、1、3、14</strong>（简中、繁中、韩、日）使用 <strong><code>lv_font_simsun_16_cjk</code></strong>。  </li>\n<li>旧版该字体由 <code>lv_font_conv</code> 生成时，<strong>韩文音节（Hangul Syllables）未完整纳入子集</strong>，例如字符串中的「?」等码点在字库中不存在，导致整句渲染失败。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"13-采取的措施\">1.3 采取的措施<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#13-采取的措施\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>新增脚本</strong>：<code>tools/scripts/gen_lv_font_simsun_16_cjk.py</code>  \n<ul>\n<li>从 <code>applications/pages/ui_strings.c</code> 抽取 <strong>lang 0、1、3、14</strong> 全部字面字符；  </li>\n<li>使用 <strong>fonttools <code>pyftsubset</code></strong> 对 <strong><code>NotoSansCJK-Regular.ttc</code></strong>（默认 face index <strong>2</strong>，Sans CJK SC，含汉字+韩文+假名）做子集；  </li>\n<li>调用 <strong><code>lv_font_conv</code></strong> 生成 <strong><code>beken378/app/lvgl/src/font/lv_font_simsun_16_cjk.c</code></strong>（16px、4bpp，与现有配置一致）。  </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>环境依赖</strong>：Node.js、<code>LV_FONT_CONV_JS</code>、<code>pyftsubset</code>（fonttools）、系统路径下的 Noto CJK TTC（可通过环境变量覆盖路径与 face index）。  </li>\n<li><strong>构建</strong>：本地已通过 <code>scons --beken=bk7252n -j8</code> 验证编译。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"14-其它脚本说明已有\">1.4 其它脚本说明（已有）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#14-其它脚本说明已有\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>tools/scripts/gen_lv_font_ui_i18n_14.py</code>：<code>ui_strings.c</code> 首条语言行在文件中为第 20 行，对应 <strong><code>splitlines()</code> 下标 <code>_ROW_BASE = 19</code></strong>；用于再生 <strong><code>lv_font_ui_i18n_14</code></strong>（DejaVu + Loma 等）。  </li>\n<li>多语言开发说明可参考：<a href=\"/notes/86d6a17041618132f76abf\">BK7252n 上 LVGL 多语言界面开发指南</a>。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"15-后续建议字库\">1.5 后续建议（字库）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#15-后续建议字库\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>修改上述四种语言的文案后，需重新运行 <strong><code>gen_lv_font_simsun_16_cjk.py</code></strong> 再编译。  </li>\n<li>uk / pt / tr / cs 若实机仍异常，应用 <strong>addr2line / 日志</strong> 锁定具体缺码或区分 NFC/NFD，再扩展 <code>gen_lv_font_ui_i18n_14</code> 子集。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"2-稳定性data-abort-与按键场景\">2. 稳定性：Data Abort 与按键场景<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#2-稳定性data-abort-与按键场景\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"21-现象\">2.1 现象<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#21-现象\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>极限按键（secondary desktop、录音起停、MQTT 收图、QR 预览、<code>audio_wait</code> 超时等）后，偶发 <strong><code>data abort</code></strong>，PC 曾落在 <strong><code>memcpy</code></strong>（须与同版本 <code>rtthread.map</code>/<code>addr2line</code> 核对）。  </li>\n<li>随后 <strong><code>shutdown</code> 与重启</strong>；未必表现为堆用量单调上升至 100%。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"22-架构层结论不写实现细节\">2.2 架构层结论（不写实现细节）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#22-架构层结论不写实现细节\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>首要怀疑</strong>：<strong>单块 MQTT 二进制共享缓冲</strong>（约 20KB）与 <strong>零拷贝</strong> 投递 —— 打印线程 <code>mqtt_prn</code>、LVGL 异步预览（<code>lv_desktop_request_show_ws_thermal_image</code>）、<strong>下一趟</strong> <code>result.start</code> 收包 <strong>共用同一物理缓冲区</strong>，在背靠背任务或超时与迟到数据交错时，易产生 <strong>覆盖仍被读取的内存</strong> → 非法访问 / <code>memcpy</code> fault。  </li>\n<li><strong>按键</strong>：作为多条异步链路的触发器，缩短会话间隔，<strong>放大竞态概率</strong>。  </li>\n<li><strong>次要</strong>：堆碎片、分配失败后未校验指针等，需与主线竞态区分排查。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"23-文档化-bug须后续彻底解决\">2.3 文档化 Bug（须后续彻底解决）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#23-文档化-bug须后续彻底解决\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"/notes/29688af9637cf23baf5a53\">Bug 收集器（BK7252n + LVGL 打印机固件）</a></strong>：Bug 收集器索引与约定。  </li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"/notes/7e757dba3afa1d4361d951\">BUG-001：按键极限操作触发 Data Abort / 意外重启</a></strong>：<strong>BUG-001</strong>，含现象、涉及文件、复现方向、<strong>关闭标准</strong>（缓冲区所有权、会话门禁、超时与异步一致、压力测试与提交记录）。  </li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"/notes/795a1a96f9c620254c9633\">AI 打印机固件开发记录</a></strong>：已增加 <strong>§8 Bug 跟踪</strong>，链接至 BUG-001。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"3-涉及路径速查\">3. 涉及路径速查<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#3-涉及路径速查\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>类型</th><th>路径</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>UI 字符串</td><td><code>applications/pages/ui_strings.c</code></td></tr><tr><td>字体路由</td><td><code>ui_strings_font()</code>（同上文件）</td></tr><tr><td>CJK 字体产物</td><td><code>beken378/app/lvgl/src/font/lv_font_simsun_16_cjk.c</code></td></tr><tr><td>CJK 再生脚本</td><td><code>tools/scripts/gen_lv_font_simsun_16_cjk.py</code></td></tr><tr><td>i18n 字体脚本</td><td><code>tools/scripts/gen_lv_font_ui_i18n_14.py</code></td></tr><tr><td>二进制接收 / 打印</td><td><code>applications/mqtt_backend/mqtt_backend_binary_rx.c</code></td></tr><tr><td>等图超时</td><td><code>applications/audio/audio_result_wait.c</code></td></tr><tr><td>WS 图预览异步</td><td><code>applications/pages/lv_example_meter.c</code></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"4-后续工作清单\">4. 后续工作清单<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#4-后续工作清单\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>BUG-001</strong>：按 <code>bug-collector</code> 中关闭标准实现缓冲所有权或会话序列化，并完成长时间压力测试。  </li>\n<li><strong>字库</strong>：文案变更后重新跑 CJK 生成脚本；uk/pt/tr/cs 实机问题按需扩展 <code>lv_font_ui_i18n_14</code> 或查运行时。  </li>\n<li><strong>回归</strong>：重大修改后对 <code>scons --beken=bk7252n</code> 与关键 UI/MQTT 路径做冒烟测试。</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<p><em>本文档为会话开发内容的汇总纪要；实现细节以仓库内源码与 Bug 单正文为准。</em></p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/6d428def14b8ffdc828f43\">AI 打印机固件 — 项目交接资料</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/62ff4545e5f1373c5cfe01\">AI 打印机固件 — 项目开发记录总纲</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"root","desc":"BK7252N AI ��ӡ���̼��ĵ���","updated":1780371367067,"created":1595961348801,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"801bb942f5d3a833cb045cb9b3abd9d0","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"������¼.��Ŀ������¼�ܸ�","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":3,"offset":96},"end":{"line":8,"column":28,"offset":121},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"������¼.��Ŀ������¼�ܸ�"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"������¼.��Ŀ��������","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":3,"offset":143},"end":{"line":9,"column":26,"offset":166},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"������¼.��Ŀ��������"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"�׶��Կ����ܽ�","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":3,"offset":187},"end":{"line":10,"column":18,"offset":202},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"�׶��Կ����ܽ�"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"tutorial","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":3,"offset":219},"end":{"line":11,"column":15,"offset":231},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"tutorial"